# Creative solution generation from De Bono's lateral thinking methods

{{PRODUCTIZE_PREAMBLE}}

Use this skill to run the Productize prompt contract for **Creative solution generation from De Bono's lateral thinking methods**.

## Instructions

1. Treat every `{{PLACEHOLDER}}` in the contract as an input to collect, infer, or mark as missing.
